#~ "<ulink url=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Portable_apps\">Portable "
#~ "software</ulink> is a class of software that is suitable for use on "
#~ "portable drives such as a USB (thumb) drive or iPod, although any "
#~ "external hard drive could theoretically be used. The concept of carrying "
#~ "one's favored applications, utilities, and files on a portable drive for "
#~ "use on any computer is one which has evolved considerably in recent years."
